data.job_description:
We need to implement a Flutter based application and are seeking a great developer for it. The main responsibilities will include writing clean code, conducting testing, integrating APIs, and optimizing performance. The minimum requirements are as follows:

3-year experience and proficiency in cross-platform development using Flutter;

understanding of basic design principles;

familiarity with APIs, JSON, and web services integration;

problem-solving and testing skills.

10 IT startups with a total capitalization of more than $15M run their products with Trood technologies. We organize cooperation with them, as well as with other promising startups in the US and Europe. For the most active and qualified developers, we offer the opportunity to participate in the development of Trood Core - a new low-code development framework.

Requirements:

hard-skills:
• ReactNative or Flutter at the professional level;
• English B1/B2;

soft-skills:
• The ability to learn and improve skills;
• Good acceptance of criticism and willingness to discuss your code;
• Care when writing and documenting code;
• Sociability, teamwork skills;
• High professional motivation and ambitions.

Nice to have:
• Experience with Java, Kotlin, Objective C, Swift;
• Experience with a Back-End stack;
• Contribution to at least one store-published app.

Scope of application:
• Development of the mobile part of the company's business applications;
• Participation in the software architecture design;
• Technical documentation design;
• Interaction with external tech teams.

Looking forward to hearing from you!
